summaries.short: The agent of the Public Prosecutor imposes strict new security measures; Teresa and Lorena reaffirm their pact.
summaries.full: The agent of the Public Prosecutor, who is investigating Capadocia, imposes strict new security measures. While Federico and La Negra breathe a sigh of relief thinking they are safe, Teresa and Lorena reaffirm their pact to help each other.

summaries.short: The arrival of a new inmate at Capadocia surprises everyone; Teresa and Victor turn up some information on Santiago's assault.
summaries.full: The arrival of a new inmate at Capadocia surprises everyone. With the help of Valeria, the psychiatrist, Teresa and Victor turn up some information that points them in the right direction to get to the bottom of the assault on Santiago, as well as other recent crimes both inside and outside the prison.

summaries.short: Victor Hernandez, the deputy prosecutor who is investigating Capadocia, becomes the headache for ECSO, and a plot gets Sandra locked up.
summaries.full: Victor Hernandez, the deputy prosecutor who is investigating Capadocia, becomes the headache for ECSO, and a plot gets Sandra locked up behind bars. Teresa warns Valeria: 'Capadocia is a black hole that devours anything in its grasp.'

summaries.full: Capadocia is under investigation: the Public Prosecutor has to clear up a crime that points in many directions, and affects the ECSO, as well as Teresa and her family. The arrival of Valeria, the new psychiatrist at the prison, is disturbing to the inmates because of her astonishing resemblance to La Bambi.

summaries.full: A prisoner at Capadocia falls into the hands of a drug kingpin and becomes part of a dangerous game, in which both sides try to use the hostage to their own ends: law enforcement wants to nail the drug dealer, while he is bargaining to recover something that belongs to him. In the end, only one side comes out ahead.

summaries.full: As the noose starts to tighten, Teresa turns to Lorena for help. Federico suspects that the lost shipment of drugs is in Capadocia and organizes a search inside the prison. Meanwhile, Andrea is victim to a scheme hatched by La Negra. Teresa hires a new psychiatrist at the institution named Valeria, who is disturbed by her own life story.
